import {HeaderIcons , HeaderLogo , HeaderNav , HeaderProfile , HedaerAdmin} from '../index.js'
import { useState } from 'react'


export default function Header(props){
   

    return(
    <header className="header">
        <section className="flex" style={header}>
            <HeaderLogo />
            <HeaderNav aboutClick={aboutClick} />
            <HeaderIcons profileClick={profileClick} />
            <HeaderProfile profile_click={profile_click}/>
        </section>
        <HedaerAdmin header_admin={header_admin} />
    </header>
    )
}
